{"tid":1218112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[廣傳]犧牲左咁多，諗清楚星期日到底要提出咩訴求","createTime":"2019-06-13T14:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T01:29:16.000Z","uid":89974,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b398f3d10d3ed7b26a8823f90810b455866e9696","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"我明白大家呢幾日情緒好緊張，好需要放鬆下，但係我地仲笑緊林鄭，睇緊警長講話既時候，有一班人而家仲係差館，係醫院入面生死未卜。<br />\n<br />\n佢地犧牲左前途，犧牲左健康，比人拉比人整傷，爭取番黎既就係呢三日既寶貴時間。<br />\n<br />\n我希望係星期日之前，各位手足要諗清楚幾個問題：<br />\n<br />\n1. 我地既訴求(非常重要)<br />\n撤回條例，向警方追究責任呢兩個一定要做，但係咁就完？777落黎上個888；下次專登整班後生仔，班專業人士同商家就未必會出黎幫手。唔好話要一勞永逸，但至少對得住犧牲前途個班人，對得住100萬人出黎反對既力量。記住訴求既前提係在有可能讓步既空間內尋求最大利益。問下你既戰友，問下大台，問下兄弟姐妹，統一大家既條件，星期日大聲講出黎。<br />\n<br />\n2.增強防禦<br />\n14年出黎無裝備，19年出黎又係無裝備，仲要比人連打幾日，甘心咩？好多手足已經比哂意見，唔出得前線既人出下力都得既。<br />\n<br />\n3.搵更多同行人<br />\n有一班人唯利是圖，見風轉陀，其實係最適合去拉攏。我地唔可以祈求所有人都係聖人，但係要令大部份人成為同路人其實唔難。建制派一直都保皇，但只要危及到佢地自身既利益佢地就陽奉陰違。同樣，只要同C9講樓價會跌，佢就會識驚；同商人講隨時會比人拉左番去清算，佢地就會出黎幫手；同教徒講係大陸信教都會比人拉，佢地就會識黎唱聖詩。呢方面就需要文宣，鍵盤戰士不斷努力。<br />\n<br />\n舉個理想化既例子，屋企有老豆老母或者再上一輩，佢地如果係錫你又同時建制味濃，就可以不斷用自己做例子，如果通過左，成個家族隨時陷家剷，財產全部充公哂。如果佢真係錫你既話，係信你同信三姑六婆之間都仲有得打。<br />\n<br />\n三吾識七個班叔父伯母就由得佢死啦。<br />\n<br />\n4.和理非唔係永遠無用<br />\n係活動期間唱歌仔和平散去就緊係無用，因為我地只會比人打到飛起。但去到後勤，國際形象，甚至善後個陣，和理非多數都會比人更好既印象，一定要收放自如。<br />\n<br />\n5.投票！<br />\n下次投票時，記住呢幾日流過既血，盡可能幫值得幫既人入去。每一個人入到去，都係減少緊後生仔每一次要流既血。<br />\n<br />\n記住而家唔係煮飯仔，好多人係搵命搏！！"},{"pid":"b02fad782a5117930bd09fbfcb410de62b304a78","tid":1218112,"uid":93986,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"撤回所有向示威者的指控同禁止秋後算賬"},{"pid":"5568c78a22946eabf68c15d9e54d22adefe204f6","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:00:57.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"983ccabb491e47a642b60aa1290e9a5ec6551f45","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:02:42.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"b57483b5d5b8fc8a78b27b0085decc873f29843e","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"4a0352f788936d9e8296a4b5fccf643f7aed27b0","tid":1218112,"uid":226955,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"只有一個，「撤回逃犯條例」"},{"pid":"4cea378c12445156718e138c5c675996ffbbc61a","tid":1218112,"uid":224095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"如有不反對通知書，其實唔會有咩大衝突"},{"pid":"89fa1c8fc6b1bf5a1d83df7969c67b907cbec56d","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:07:43.000Z","msg":"我其實最擔心既係，撤回一次，下次整條剩係玩死後生仔既例，就無咁多人上街。<br />\n<br />\n再市懀咁講，如果剩係撤回條例，我覺得對唔住100萬人出黎行兩日，同十幾個人比人拉。<br />\n<br />\n當然呢個只係一家之言，大家各有各想法"},{"pid":"890a811daad3167e051affba964ed927b2103863","tid":1218112,"uid":236878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b02fad782a5117930bd09fbfcb410de62b304a78","tid":1218112,"uid":93986,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T14:57:29.000Z","msg":"撤回所有向示威者的指控同禁止秋後算賬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:09:04.000Z","msg":"真 呢個我自己覺得係除咗撤回修例最重要 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fb4bc6dd81e2a53c2257c0e806bf30934877c8","tid":1218112,"uid":240628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:09:40.000Z","msg":"[廣傳][長文]長期革命，每個人都要準備對抗催淚彈/胡椒噴霧必須用品<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/OeDsoU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/OeDsoU</a>"},{"pid":"aae781b39c3f1a209c454239b938fbcd4fa40a38","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:10:14.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"97cc57f33e919c9a631e5fea9ea4631d87497c00","tid":1218112,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"撤回逃犯條例<br />\n林鄭下台<br />\n盧偉聰下台"},{"pid":"2d88fb9f865e17d4443cf1429222218bd0a04ec6","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:14:34.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"54eab83a4dc257f6f80dba18f6fa32bb70e06725","tid":1218112,"uid":105976,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:14:38.000Z","msg":"1.撤回送中 <br />\n<br />\n2.追究警方濫用暴力 <br />\n盧偉聰, 負責612行動指揮官 下台<br />\n開槍打記者, 室內放催淚彈,<br />\n槍口瞄腿以上 射擊和平示威者  革職 , 告謀殺 <br />\n<br />\n 3.反警權過大<br />\n必需配備委任證 特警裝備都係<br />\n冇合理懷疑唔需要俾身份證佢查<br />\n<br />\n 4.修改不合時公安條例<br />\n 還人民集會自由<br />\n<br />\n5. 改善警察質素低下 <br />\n唔再請垃圾做黑警  起碼U grad<br />\n<br />\n6.高官議員財政披露防貪污<br />\n<br />\n7. 真普選 雙普選   取消功能組別"},{"pid":"57cbd1f92f4aaf72b80073e992ff52a1dbb82efb","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:17:32.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"915ada1f46ef856835e384e624509323a07a4089","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:18:36.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"add5d4c6b0e98c298f9d4572631675def25aa7bd","tid":1218112,"uid":195983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:21:09.000Z","msg":"支持學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fe7b05a16a37bca76812d746a3277cceba2deeb","tid":1218112,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:21:46.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"af67cf842b03a598576f6aa6ceaa2af984f87d8f","tid":1218112,"uid":4942,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:22:43.000Z","msg":"唔需要太多<br />\n<br />\n集中火力，撒回送中修訂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果撒佢都一定要下台謝罪<br />\n<br />\n另外可以譴責警察使用過份武力"},{"pid":"54b8d792020c796ef9dae16ae181f8875eb0942d","tid":1218112,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">614 油油行動 正式啟動 </span><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊入黎發夢，幫手推同share出去<br />\n<br />\n614 油油行動 正式啟動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1217162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1217162</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"26cc1446d3cf1c01df670f3806d1925bdacb1966","tid":1218112,"uid":7948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBehmVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBehmVj.png&h=74ea6e13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e24e1f19015045ed30bc9b8619133aa0b5bd01e8","tid":1218112,"uid":77368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"釋放被捕人士"},{"pid":"351cc6b864fe0cf09b53d627a21a911d280983b5","tid":1218112,"uid":258927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:25:08.000Z","msg":"呢幾日我都諗緊呢個問題... <br />\n依家政府每次推出惡法, 市民就反抗, 好似頭痛醫頭, 腳痛醫腳咁.<br />\nLoop 到天荒地老, 最好既結果都只係延長香港既死亡時間, 但長此落去, 香港始終會死. <br />\n到底點先可以擺脫呢個困局?<br />\n<br />\n所有既矛盾, 都係97之後, 政權變更所以出現. <br />\n當然, 香港無可能回到97前. 咁但係, 無法回去係咪代表我地只能繼續用依家呢套? 一次又一次遊行, 一次又一次落台, 然後繼續俾一堆689, 777, 999 扯住我地個鼻行?<br />\n<br />\n既然依家呢套唔 work, 係咪應該諗下其他方法? 真普選係一個. 雙普選係一個. 但呢2個推唔郁既, 會唔會有第三, 第四, 第五套方案? 或者由結構上改變, 整個民選既副行政長官出黎?<br />\n<br />\n我對政治無乜認識, 只係唔想睇住我地既家一日一日咁破敗落去咋... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e661cf3a55b3eb11b668a6f49b905faa88e812ec","tid":1218112,"uid":77542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:25:45.000Z","msg":"撤回逃犯條例<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n越簡單越顯示我哋理直氣壯"},{"pid":"bed09e6d03cfd0ad7a4fcb6a9256f7f7dc3cecc4","tid":1218112,"uid":44722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}